{"tid":113994,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分手後別妄想做返朋友","createTime":"2017-02-09T12:13:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T15:45:09.000Z","uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9016993562136ae21739d2bf20d5add26ece42ee","tid":113994,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:13:18.000Z","msg":"同佢分左手一段時間<br />\n冇可能復合返但大家都好唔捨得大家<br />\n所以我地做返朋友<br />\n通常都係我搵佢<br />\n問吓佢呢排點<br />\n點知佢根本唔記得我地分左手<br />\n講唔夠2句就發我脾氣<br />\n例如我得閒先搵佢吹水 點解我唔係秒覆佢等等<br />\n有似我話同另一個女性朋友愈行愈埋<br />\n佢表面祝福 希望我地幸福<br />\n但佢講唔夠兩句又話我淨係顧住溝其他女唔理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又或者淨係日日同朋友見唔覆whatsapp <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都分左手一段時間啦<br />\n點解你仍然expect咁多？<br />\n係你唔肯同返我一齊咋<br />\n你想我點呀？我而家開始放低你有返自己生活你又唔滿意？痴撚線？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e4763074fc00f69a64797dd7d18dcaf1e9e3fb3","tid":113994,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:15:35.000Z","msg":"復原後不要再度跟你做朋友<br />\n我怕我念舊&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b89facf299d1d7b81b3dc0f912910dbfd262797f","tid":113994,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:16:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>復原後不要再度跟你做朋友<br />\n我怕我念舊&amp;nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解普通朋友都唔做得？<br />\n其實大家降低返對大家既期望就唔會搞成咁"},{"pid":"975647594a34eb015ef8f445e264122be3643115","tid":113994,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:17:10.000Z","msg":"你無故行了兇又不忍心　置傷者不顧<br />\n你接球接得辛苦<br />\n我發球也發得痛苦<br />\n誰多此一愛　在陷害無辜<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c704877d58e163b6e3756669905ac9bf37e1a27","tid":113994,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:18:51.000Z","msg":"同你調轉係個男既唔記得左係自己講分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb8bb1fb3f5367bc441dcdd04f792090f431c72","tid":113994,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:19:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>復原後不要再度跟你做朋友<br />\n我怕我念舊&amp;nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解普通朋友都唔做得？<br />\n其實大家降低返對大家既期望就唔會搞成咁</blockquote><br />\n短時間内根本唔會得<br />\n時間耐左淡左可能得<br />\n但其中一方都可能唔得然後諗多左<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdbe5eae432ff47873594b296f0d080b93388e45","tid":113994,"uid":5232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:19:30.000Z","msg":"下次等我眼淚流盡又愛你<br />\n我會預備 受傷的勇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dbbd041096d39e758371ada43d4f952ee87efcb","tid":113994,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:41:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>復原後不要再度跟你做朋友<br />\n我怕我念舊&amp;nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解普通朋友都唔做得？<br />\n其實大家降低返對大家既期望就唔會搞成咁</blockquote><br />\n短時間内根本唔會得<br />\n時間耐左淡左可能得<br />\n但其中一方都可能唔得然後諗多左<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要幾耐？其實都分左手幾個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6fb32539c10eb1133eecd0f1acd0156ddccc7bb","tid":113994,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:42:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同你調轉係個男既唔記得左係自己講分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMore <br />\n巴打你仲有冇同佢做朋友？"},{"pid":"05f4edd6cb4e7d0c2767eb0e9d7e1b763ad9b786","tid":113994,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:44:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你無故行了兇又不忍心　置傷者不顧<br />\n你接球接得辛苦<br />\n我發球也發得痛苦<br />\n誰多此一愛　在陷害無辜<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAgger<br />\n繼續維持落去大家都好痛苦<br />\n但唔搵大家好掛住又痛苦<br />\n唔肯放手 繼續拖 好幼稚 但冇放手既勇氣<br />\n尤其遲d可能會約出黎食飯<br />\n分左手之後都冇見過佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ba076895fd1f60368669ede0c13f971e716983","tid":113994,"uid":31317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T13:13:03.000Z","msg":"你講得岩<br />\n原來係期望<br />\n<br />\n一開始同ex做返朋友仲會期望<br />\n後來慢慢出多幾次街<br />\n感覺開始慢慢變淡<br />\n而家調整左心態 企返出黎睇佢係一個點既人<br />\n就終於知道大家係完全冇可能一齊 <br />\n火星撞地球 其實做朋友都幾困難添"},{"pid":"259f981f8ad1057d8c62c54746b6e5085bd587e6","tid":113994,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T13:29:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同你調轉係個男既唔記得左係自己講分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMore <br />\n巴打你仲有冇同佢做朋友？</blockquote><br />\n分手兩個月之後佢返黎想復合<br />\n我話唔得 之後佢就話身邊連一個朋友都無好孤獨<br />\n咁我就話我唔介意做你朋友(個時真係唔介意)<br />\n但佢拒絕<br />\n<br />\n咁我同佢分手之後都有同返之前因為佢而斷左聯絡既男性朋友聯絡返<br />\n仲同佢地傾得幾開心(打機gp黎有男有女)<br />\n有時仲會長on wtsapp同班人傾計<br />\n呢個時候佢就發癲啦 問我做咩掛住同第二個男仔傾計 又話呷醋呀 我係屬於佢架唔准走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢煩鳩左我三個月 日日審犯咁審我今日同邊個傾左啲咩<br />\n大佬呀 分左手架啦 仲要係你分<br />\n屌你老母你唔好咁痴線啦<br />\n到最後終於頂唔順block左佢<br />\n<br />\n朋友喎 屌你老母啦"},{"pid":"2ba95a181b4d63b354db13ba3c2b5ccad2f843ac","tid":113994,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T13:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n朋友都冇得我做"},{"pid":"c36fa94eee6f354e70eb154283bc8e4a570a5bd6","tid":113994,"uid":49722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T13:44:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同佢分左手一段時間<br />\n冇可能復合返但大家都好唔捨得大家<br />\n所以我地做返朋友<br />\n通常都係我搵佢<br />\n問吓佢呢排點<br />\n點知佢根本唔記得我地分左手<br />\n講唔夠2句就發我脾氣<br />\n例如我得閒先搵佢吹水 點解我唔係秒覆佢等等<br />\n有似我話同另一個女性朋友愈行愈埋<br />\n佢表面祝福 希望我地幸福<br />\n但佢講唔夠兩句又話我淨係顧住溝其他女唔理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又或者淨係日日同朋友見唔覆whatsapp <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都分左手一段時間啦<br />\n點解你仍然expect咁多？<br />\n係你唔肯同返我一齊咋<br />\n你想我點呀？我而家開始放低你有返自己生活你又唔滿意？痴撚線？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ni know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b530dc384446caa97cc9fe99ff08f9bc84fd94","tid":113994,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T13:46:07.000Z","msg":"咁係因為佢個心仲有你"},{"pid":"711c23fbbbfef406a7f3831d78ec7c48518724e7","tid":113994,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T13:47:39.000Z","msg":"我不堅強分手後別做朋友"},{"pid":"02397d5f5f7477454ab0028bfc5cd214933c5d99","tid":113994,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:32:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你講得岩<br />\n原來係期望<br />\n<br />\n一開始同ex做返朋友仲會期望<br />\n後來慢慢出多幾次街<br />\n感覺開始慢慢變淡<br />\n而家調整左心態 企返出黎睇佢係一個點既人<br />\n就終於知道大家係完全冇可能一齊 <br />\n火星撞地球 其實做朋友都幾困難添</blockquote><br />\nAgger 我都覺<br />\n火星撞地球 就算大家都有感覺都無謂夾硬起返埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反正都冇結果<br />\n但佢明知冇機一齊但點解仲可以係我身上期望咁多？<br />\n大佬 我唔記得你講過既野你又話我唔重視你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你肯放手未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我淨係想做朋友咋"},{"pid":"5884da51482cbb95bb603d571ee31b9e472d9a7c","tid":113994,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:36:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁係因為佢個心仲有你</blockquote><br />\n我知呀<br />\n但佢都唔可以咁自私呀？<br />\n當初我為佢做咩都得<br />\n佢就同我分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫我死心<br />\n又堅決唔復合<br />\nDllm 而家又仲當我係佢條仔咁 搵親都發我脾氣<br />\n唔据我唔重視佢係咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa7a8cb88d05bf1d111806ef422c6dddee545b4","tid":113994,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:39:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同你調轉係個男既唔記得左係自己講分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMore <br />\n巴打你仲有冇同佢做朋友？</blockquote><br />\n分手兩個月之後佢返黎想復合<br />\n我話唔得 之後佢就話身邊連一個朋友都無好孤獨<br />\n咁我就話我唔介意做你朋友(個時真係唔介意)<br />\n但佢拒絕<br />\n<br />\n咁我同佢分手之後都有同返之前因為佢而斷左聯絡既男性朋友聯絡返<br />\n仲同佢地傾得幾開心(打機gp黎有男有女)<br />\n有時仲會長on wtsapp同班人傾計<br />\n呢個時候佢就發癲啦 問我做咩掛住同第二個男仔傾計 又話呷醋呀 我係屬於佢架唔准走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢煩鳩左我三個月 日日審犯咁審我今日同邊個傾左啲咩<br />\n大佬呀 分左手架啦 仲要係你分<br />\n屌你老母你唔好咁痴線啦<br />\n到最後終於頂唔順block左佢<br />\n<br />\n朋友喎 屌你老母啦</blockquote><br />\nAgger I know that feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都覺勁撚on9 <br />\n都唔係男女朋友關係你憑咩要求咁多？<br />\n但你忍左3個月先分手好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我唔會block<br />\n因為無論佢幾仆街都好我都仍然想同佢維繫落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de35f5e1e1b892de396717719de8d114ebdbba94","tid":113994,"uid":51308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:11:35.000Z","msg":"男女都一樣 <br />\n<br />\n我都唔係放得低曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb880f041b553ae5245165886b283817357e9e4","tid":113994,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:13:13.000Z","msg":"當然啦"},{"pid":"4750cdc1c2a7d943313043ca3da1f7b35f083e0e","tid":113994,"uid":83165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T17:41:21.000Z","msg":"只要有一方仲有幻想有期望，就無可能做得返朋友<br />\n自摺以後唔好見算數<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">通常嗰個係我</span>"},{"pid":"3322df93e